   <conbody>
      <p class="- topic/p ">Rotating the direction control lever changes the speed of travel. With
                                handle rotated counter (D) clockwise(towards the operator), the lift
                                truck is in FIRST speed.</p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">Rotate the lever clockwise(away from the operator) for the SECOND and
                                THIRD speeds. Do not fail to place the forward-reverse lever in the
                                neutral position before starting the engine.</p>
   </conbody>
